    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Inti Bangun Sejahtera Tbk provides telecommunication network services in the information, communication, and technology (ITC) sector in Indonesia. The company operates through two segments: Telecommunication Tower Lease and Network Equipment and Bandwidth Lease segments. The company offers built-to-suit, a rental space BTS; co-location rental space; semi BTS hotel and MCP; metro-e, a high-capacity data network solution; and clustered base indoor and outdoor coverage service solution with indoor -distributed antenna system and outdoor-distributed antenna system. It also offers internet interconnection, SMS content, and multimedia services; and is involved in data processing, consulting management activities, and real estate property rental, as well as civil, mechanical, and electrical works. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Kudus, Indonesia. PT Inti Bangun Sejahtera Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT iForte Solusi Infotek.",
